title: Rare Prints // Russian Dolls
description:
Ray-Ban is proud to present the RARE PRINTS special series. 

As you can guess from the name, these are no ordinary sunglasses. This special series collection combines colorful new patterns with the original Wayfarer design.

For each Rare Prints collection, we collaborated with some of the world's top print makers and asked them to design a poster inspired by a unique pattern.
 
Those prints went on to inspire six one-of-a-kind films where the artwork come to life.
